w.brainpickings.org/2012/09/21/hermann-hesse-trees/?mc_cid=3D6c73834c6e&mc=
_eid=3D[UNIQID]) =2C then couldn=E2=80=99t think=2C couldn=E2=80=99t feel=
=2E

I=E2=80=99ve been unable to return to the park in the weeks since. But I=
=E2=80=99ve returned to one of my few other sources of constancy and comfo=
rt =E2=80=94 The Journal of Henry David Thoreau=2C 1837=E2=80=931861 (http=
