nt;">While fame impedes and constricts=2C obscurity wraps about a man like=
 a mist; obscurity is dark=2C ample=2C and free; obscurity lets the mind t=
ake its way unimpeded. Over the obscure man is poured the merciful suffusi=
on of darkness. None knows where he goes or comes. He may seek the truth a=
nd speak it; he alone is free; he alone is truthful; he alone is at peace.=
</p></blockquote><p style=3D"-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;-ms-text-size-=
adjust: 100%;color: #262626;font-family: Georgia=2C serif;font-size: 15px;=
line-height: 175%;text-align: left;">Extolling the value of obscurity as=
