roubling Love</em>=E2=80=A6 You asked the question ironically=2C with one=
 of your bemused expressions=E2=80=A6 I do not intend to do anything for <=
em>Troubling Love</em>=2C anything that might involve the public engagemen=
t of me personally. I=E2=80=99ve already done enough for this long story:=
 I wrote it. If the book is worth anything=2C that should be sufficient. I=
 won=E2=80=99t participate in discussions and conferences=2C if I=E2=80=99=
m invited. I won=E2=80=99t go and accept prizes=2C if any are awarded to m=
e. I will never promote the book=2C especially on television=2C not in Ita=
ly or=2C as the case may be=2C abroad. I will be interviewed only in writi=
ng=2C but I would prefer to limit even that to the indispensable minimum.=
 I am absolutely committed in this sense to myself and my family. I hope n=
ot to be forced to change my mind.</p><p style=3D"-webkit-text-size-adjust=
